          Trade Agent Skills<br>
          <span class="bg-gradient-to-r from-yellow-400 to-orange-500 bg-clip-text text-transparent">Securely</span>
        </h1>

        <!-- Problem Statement -->
        <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-blue-100 mb-8 max-w-3xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
          Stop risking malware and unreliable agents. Our marketplace ensures every transaction is audited, 
